#. <section class="sutta" id="sn35.24"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn35.24:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 35"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 35"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.24:0.2"
msgid "3. Sabbavagga"
msgstr "3. All"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn35.24:0.3"
msgid "24. Pahānasutta"
msgstr "24. Giving Up"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.16"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: Sabbappahānāya → sabbaṃ pahānāya (s1-3, km, mr)
msgctxt "sn35.24:1.1"
msgid "“Sabbappahānāya vo, bhikkhave, dhammaṃ desessāmi."
msgstr "“Mendicants, I will teach you the principle for giving up the all."

msgctxt "sn35.24:1.2"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha."
msgstr "Listen …"

msgctxt "sn35.24:1.3"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, sabbappahānāya dhammo?"
msgstr "And what is the principle for giving up the all?"

# Note the use of samphassapaccaya here instead of samphassaja
msgctxt "sn35.24:1.4"
msgid ""
"Cakkhuṃ, bhikkhave, pahātabbaṃ, rūpā pahātabbā, cakkhuviññāṇaṃ pahātabbaṃ, "
"cakkhusamphasso pahātabbo, yampidaṃ cakkhusamphassapaccayā uppajjati "
"vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā adukkhamasukhaṃ vā tampi pahātabbaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""
"The eye should be given up. Sights should be given up. Eye consciousness "
"should be given up. Eye contact should be given up. The painful, pleasant, "
"or neutral feeling that arises conditioned by eye contact should also be "
"given up. "

msgctxt "sn35.24:1.5"
msgid ""
msgstr "The ear … nose …"

msgctxt "sn35.24:1.6"
msgid ""
"jivhā pahātabbā, rasā pahātabbā, jivhāviññāṇaṃ pahātabbaṃ, jivhāsamphasso "
"pahātabbo, yampidaṃ jivhāsamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā "
"dukkhaṃ vā adukkhamasukhaṃ vā tampi pahātabbaṃ."
msgstr "tongue …"

msgctxt "sn35.24:1.7"
msgid "Kāyo pahātabbo …"
msgstr "body …"

msgctxt "sn35.24:1.8"
msgid ""
"mano pahātabbo, dhammā pahātabbā, manoviññāṇaṃ pahātabbaṃ, manosamphasso "
"pahātabbo, yampidaṃ manosamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā "
"dukkhaṃ vā adukkhamasukhaṃ vā tampi pahātabbaṃ."
msgstr ""
"mind should be given up. Thoughts should be given up. Mind consciousness "
"should be given up. Mind contact should be given up. The painful, pleasant, "
"or neutral feeling that arises conditioned by mind contact should be given "
"up."

msgctxt "sn35.24:1.9"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, bhikkhave, sabbappahānāya dhammo”ti."
msgstr "This is the principle for giving up the all.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.24:1.10"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
